iously – with astonishing results</p><p class="sc-52df2991-0 sc-52df2991-12 gHVKSt iDaMRq">Julia Hejduk</p></div><div class="sc-52df2991-6 enIxgZ"></div></div></a><a href="/essays/how-breast-cancer-rips-up-conventional-markers-of-gender"><div type="essay" class="sc-52df2991-9 kGHAoy"><div type="essay" src="https://epsilon.aeon.co/images/0ae61bb8-e7e5-4734-8f07-c427917e08ea/card_rtscdu9q.jpg" class="sc-73aaa9a5-2 iVVwRQ"><img alt="Rubens painting Venus and Cupid reimagined with Venus on the left gazing in a mirror at her mastectomized breast. A cherub like Cupid to the right holds the mirror" loading="lazy" width="720" height="288" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" style="color:transparent" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, (max-width: 1200px) 50vw, 33vw" srcSet="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fepsilon.aeon.co%2Fimages%2F0ae61bb8-e7e5-4734-8f07-c427917e08ea%2Fcard_rtscdu9q.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=90 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fepsilon.aeon.co%2Fimages%2F0ae61bb8-e7e5-4734-8f07-c427917e08ea%2Fcard_rtscdu9q.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=90 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fepsilon.aeon.co%2Fimages%2F0ae61bb8-e7e5-4734-8f07-c427917e08ea%2Fcard_rtscdu9q.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=90 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fepsilon.aeon.co%2Fimages%2F0ae61bb8-e7e5-4734-8f07-c427917e08ea%2Fcard_rtscdu9q.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=90 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fepsilon.aeon.co%2Fimages%2F0ae61bb8-e7e5-4734-8f07-c427917e08ea%2Fcard_rtscdu9q.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=90 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fepsilon.aeon.co%2Fimages%2F0ae61bb8-e7e5-4734-8f07-c427917e08ea%2Fcard_rtscdu9q.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=90 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fepsilon.aeon.co%2Fimages%2F0ae61bb8-e7e5-4734-8f07-c427917e08ea%2Fcard_rtscdu9q.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=90 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fepsilon.aeon.co%2Fimages%2F0ae61bb8-e7e5-4734-8f07-c427917e08ea%2Fcard_rtscdu9q.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=90 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fepsilon.aeon.co%2Fimages%2F0ae61bb8-e7e5-4734-8f07-c427917e08ea%2Fcard_rts